   617â†’
   618â†’You may pull in just the part of this semver utility that you need if you
   619â†’are sensitive to packing and tree-shaking concerns.  The main
   620â†’`require('semver')` export uses getter functions to lazily load the parts
   621â†’of the API that are used.
   622â†’
   623â†’The following modules are available:
   624â†’
   625â†’* `require('semver')`
   626â†’* `require('semver/classes')`
   627â†’* `require('semver/classes/comparator')`
   628â†’* `require('semver/classes/range')`
   629â†’* `require('semver/classes/semver')`
   630â†’* `require('semver/functions/clean')`
   631â†’* `require('semver/functions/cmp')`
   632â†’* `require('semver/functions/coerce')`
